<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>SkillUp Activation Email</title>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <style type="text/css">
    /* Base */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-width: 100%;
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      color: #4a4a4a;
    }
    a {
      color: #007bff;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    h1, h2, p {
      margin: 0 0 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ffffff;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #007bff;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    table td {
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    /* Layout */
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .email-header {
      background-color: #007bff;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 5px solid #ffd700;
    }
    .email-body {
      padding: 30px 30px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-bottom: 5px solid #f2f2f2;
    }
    .email-footer {
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999999;
    }
    .email-footer a {
      color: #007bff;
    }
    /* Buttons */
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: center;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    }
    .button:hover {
      background-color: #0056b3;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="email-header">
      <h1>Welcome to SkillUp!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
      <p>Hello <strong><%= user.name %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for joining SkillUp! To complete your registration, please use the following activation code:</p>
      <h2><strong><%= activationCode %></strong></h2>
      <p>Enter this code on our <a href="https://www.skillup.com/activate" style="color: #007bff;">activation page</a> within the next 5 minutes to activate your account.</p>
      <p>If you did not sign up for a SkillUp account, please disregard this email.</p>
      <a href="https://www.skillup.com/activate" class="button">Activate Your Account</a>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
      <p>If you have any questions, feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:ladanitejas12@gmail.com">ladanitejas12@gmail.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>